隨著《少年Jump》雜誌的誕生，碧日傳媒新成立了一個出版品牌「少年Jump」，專門出版少年漫畫的[[單行本|單行本]]，品項包含在《少年Jump》雜誌上連載的漫畫，以及其他碧日取得授權的少年漫畫<ref>{{cite web|last=Alverson|first=Brigid|url=https://www.publishersweekly.com/pw/by-topic/digital/content-and-e-books/article/46738-viz-app-brings-manga-to-the-ipad.html|title=Viz App Brings Manga to the iPad|publisher=[[出版者周刊|Publishers Weekly]]|date=2011-04-05|accessdate=2020-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110913150057/http://www.publishersweekly.com/pw/by-topic/digital/content-and-e-books/article/46738-viz-app-brings-manga-to-the-ipad.html|archive-date=2011-09-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另一個漫畫品牌「少年Jump進階」（{{lang|en|Shonen Jump Advanced}}）於2005年4月創辦，出版物包含更多題材偏成熟的作品，以年紀較大的青少年和[[青年|青年]]為目標讀者群<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.icv2.com/articles/news/6166.html |title=Shonen Jump Advanced Line Targets Older Teens |publisher=ICv2 |date=2004-12-20 |accessdate=2008-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080803203050/http://www.icv2.com/articles/news/6166.html |archive-date=2008-08-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Reid|first=Calvin|url=https://www.publishersweekly.com/pw/by-topic/1-legacy/24-comic-book-reviews/article/12945-viz-speeds-up-naruto-releases.html|title=Viz Debuts Shonen Jump Advanced|publisher=[[出版者周刊|Publishers Weekly]]|date=2005-01-03|accessdate=2020-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191010043449/https://www.publishersweekly.com/pw/by-topic/1-legacy/24-comic-book-reviews/article/12945-viz-speeds-up-naruto-releases.html|archive-date=2019-10-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2005年10月，碧日傳媒成立了「少年Jump家用媒體」（{{lang|en|Shonen Jump Home Video}}）品牌，發行日本動畫和《少年Jump》連載漫畫的[[原創動畫錄影帶|OVA]]<ref name="HomeVid Launch">{{cite press release |url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2005-10-14/viz-launches-shonen-jump-home-video |title=Viz Launches Shonen Jump Home Video |publisher=[[動畫新聞網|Anime News Network]] |date=2005-10-14 |accessdate=2008-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080604112804/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2005-10-14/viz-launches-shonen-jump-home-video |archive-date=2008-06-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2006年，碧日傳媒宣布成立新品牌「SJ小說」（{{lang|en|SJ Fiction}}），隸屬於碧日旗下的碧日小說（{{lang|en|Viz Fiction}}）部門。「SJ小說」專門出版《少年Jump》連載漫畫的相關[[輕小說|輕小說]]作品。<ref>{{cite press release |url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2006-09-15/viz-media-announces-three-new-fiction-novels |title=Viz Media Announces Three New Fiction Novels |publisher=[[動畫新聞網|Anime News Network]] |date=2006-09-15 |accessdate=2008-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080803212607/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2006-09-15/viz-media-announces-three-new-fiction-novels |archive-date=2008-08-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vizmedia.com/products/products.php?format_id=5&brand_id=36 |title=SJ Fiction |publisher=[[碧日|Viz Media]] |accessdate=2008-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080705190208/http://www.vizmedia.com/products/products.php?format_id=5&brand_id=36 |archive-date=2008-07-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>至於「SJ檔案」（{{lang|en|SJ Profiles}}）則負責發行《少年Jump》連載漫畫的公式漫迷手冊（fan books）、資料集（data books），以及其他相關書籍；至於美術畫集則由「SJ美術」（{{lang|en|Art of SJ}}）出版<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vizmedia.com/products/products.php?format_id=5&brand_id=30 |title=SJ Profiles |publisher=[[碧日|Viz Media]] |accessdate=2008-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080705190304/http://www.vizmedia.com/products/products.php?format_id=5&brand_id=30 |archive-date=2008-07-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vizmedia.com/products/products.php?format_id=5&brand_id=34 |title=Art of SJ |publisher=[[碧日|Viz Media]] |accessdate=2008-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080705190158/http://www.vizmedia.com/products/products.php?format_id=5&brand_id=34 |archive-date=2008-07-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 發行量與讀者群 ==

《少年Jump》的創刊號賣出超過30萬份，遠遠超過碧日傳媒原本預期的10萬份，成為2002年最暢銷的漫畫出版品之一。創刊號首刷25萬份在開賣前就供不應求，補印了2次才完全滿足市場需求。<ref name="IC First Issue">{{cite web|url=http://www.icv2.com/articles/news/2124.html |title=Shonen Jump #1 in Third Printing |publisher=ICv2 |date=2002-12-10 |accessdate=2008-07-01 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5fSzfdxpS?url=http://www.icv2.com/articles/news/2124.html |archivedate=2009-03-22 }}</ref>創刊號出版後，雜誌每期的平均發行量為19萬份，但到了創刊滿1年時就已經飆升至30萬5千份。《少年Jump》2003年8月號附贈有即將推出的《[[遊戲王|遊戲王]]》电腦游戏[[游戏演示|試玩]]，結果銷售量達到了54萬份，創下紀錄。<ref name="IC Sales">{{cite web |url=http://www.icv2.com/articles/news/3867.html |title=Shonen Jump Sales Skyrocket to 305,000! |publisher=ICv2 |date=2003-11-13 |accessdate=2008-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080803203307/http://www.icv2.com/articles/news/3867.html |archive-date=2008-08-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>到了2004年7月，雜誌的發行量大約維持在30萬份左右，穩坐北美最暢銷的日本漫畫雜誌寶座<ref>{{cite news |last=Macdonald |first=Christopher |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2004-07-13/japanese-magazine-circulation |title=Japanese Magazine Circulation |publisher=[[動畫新聞網|Anime News Network]] |date=2004-07-13 |accessdate=2020-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190525024936/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2004-07-13/japanese-magazine-circulation |archive-date=2019-05-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2006年初又上升至35萬份<ref>{{cite news |last=Macdonald |first=Christopher |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2006-01-12/japanese-manga-anthology-circulation-falling |title=Japanese Manga Anthology Circulation Falling |publisher=[[動畫新聞網|Anime News Network]] |date=2006-01-12 |accessdate=2020-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190508142036/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2006-01-12/japanese-manga-anthology-circulation-falling |archive-date=2019-05-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2008年，雜誌的平均發行量落在21萬5千份，其中54%來自訂戶[[訂閱|訂閱]]<ref name="Viz2008PK">{{cite press release |url=http://www.shonenjump.com/mediakit/images/SJ_MEDIAKIT_Web.pdf |publisher=[[碧日|Viz Media]] |title=Shonen Jump Media Kit |year=2008 |accessdate=2008-06-29 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080920214013/http://www.shonenjump.com/mediakit/images/SJ_MEDIAKIT_Web.pdf |archivedate=2008-09-20 }}</ref>。之後雜誌的訂戶量有所下降，2009年5月報導的平均發行量是20萬份<ref>{{cite web|last=Reid|first=Calvin|url=https://www.publishersweekly.com/pw/by-topic/new-titles/adult-announcements/article/16404-viz-media-launches-ikki-new-online-magazine-venture.html|title=Viz Cancels 'Shojo Beat' Manga Teen Mag|publisher=[[出版者周刊|Publishers Weekly]]|date=2009-05-20|accessdate=2020-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130910062347/http://www.publishersweekly.com/pw/by-topic/new-titles/adult-announcements/article/16404-viz-media-launches-ikki-new-online-magazine-venture.html|archive-date=2013-09-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Cha|first=Kai-Ming|url=https://www.publishersweekly.com/pw/by-topic/new-titles/adult-announcements/article/16404-viz-media-launches-ikki-new-online-magazine-venture.html|title=Viz Media Launches IKKI, New Online Magazine Venture|publisher=[[出版者周刊|Publishers Weekly]]|date=2009-05-21|accessdate=2020-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130910062347/http://www.publishersweekly.com/pw/by-topic/new-titles/adult-announcements/article/16404-viz-media-launches-ikki-new-online-magazine-venture.html|archive-date=2013-09-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>，至2010年底，雜誌每期的發行量大約是10萬左右，還算是不錯<ref name="PWFacelift">{{cite web|last=Cha|first=Kai-Ming|url=https://www.publishersweekly.com/pw/by-topic/digital/content-and-e-books/article/45143-viz-s-shonen-jump-magazine-gets-facelift-online-and-off.html|title=Viz's 'Shonen Jump' Magazine Gets Facelift Online and Off|publisher=[[出版者周刊|Publishers Weekly]]|date=2010-11-11|accessdate=2020-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101217232538/http://www.publishersweekly.com/pw/by-topic/digital/content-and-e-books/article/45143-viz-s-shonen-jump-magazine-gets-facelift-online-and-off.html|archive-date=2010-12-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

雖然雜誌的目標讀者群是10多歲的青少年，不過根據碧日傳媒於2008年提供的資料，雜誌的男性讀者僅佔了64%，女性讀者和成人讀者並不在少數，分別佔了全體讀者的36%和37%。讀者年齡的[[中位數|中位數]]為16歲，且有超過一半的讀者年齡介於13到17歲之間。官方調查顯示，在未成年讀者中，女性讀者的年齡層偏低，中位數為12歲。<ref name="Viz2008PK" />

== 迴響 ==

《少年Jump》有北美最成功且最受歡迎的日本漫畫雜誌之稱<ref name="HomeVid Launch" />，除了擁有空前絕後的發行量之外，雜誌銷量也是居高不下。雜誌收錄的漫畫作品中有許多成了暢銷書，光是其中的《[[火影忍者|火影忍者]]》單行本就獨佔了2006年北美日本漫畫總銷量的一成左右<ref name="HomeVid Launch" /><ref name="Quill">{{cite web | url=http://www.icv2.com/articles/home/9450.html | title=Naruto Nabs Quill Award | publisher=ICv2 | date=2006-10-12 | accessdate=2008-04-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110611074914/http://www.icv2.com/articles/home/9450.html | archive-date=2011-06-11 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2002年12月，《少年Jump》榮獲ICv2獎的「年度最佳漫畫產品」，原因包含其創下前所未有的高銷量，以及成功透過與[[卡通頻道|卡通頻道]]合作和贈品，將漫畫與電視媒介及當紅的《[[遊戲王|遊戲王]]》[[交換卡片遊戲|交換卡片遊戲]]緊密結合<ref name="IC Award">{{cite web |url=http://www.icv2.com/articles/news/2179.html |title=ICv2 2002 Comic Awards, Part 1 |publisher=ICv2 |date=2002-12-29 |accessdate=2008-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080725014616/http://www.icv2.com/articles/news/2179.html |archive-date=2008-07-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2009年，《少年Jump》獲得[[Anime_Expo|日本動畫振興協會獎]]的「最佳出版物獎」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2009-07-03/2009-spja-industry-award-winners-announced|publisher=Anime news Network|title=Naruto SPJA Industry Award Winners Announced at Anime Expo|date=2009-07-03|accessdate=2009-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110628225000/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2009-07-03/2009-spja-industry-award-winners-announced|archive-date=2011-06-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

評論家對編輯部選擇連載漫畫的眼光，以及每期收錄的各種文章給予好評<ref name="Jakala" /><ref name="Douresseaux" />。創刊初期，[[動畫新聞網|動畫新聞網]]的約翰·賈卡拉（{{lang|en|John Jakala}}）撰文表示，他將《少年Jump》的創刊號和其競爭對手《{{link-en|雷神Comics|Raijin Comics}}》的創刊號進行了比較，由《少年Jump》勝出。賈卡拉預言，《少年Jump》將憑藉著高品質的內容和高[[性價比|CP值]]在北美勢如破竹<ref name="Jakala">{{cite web |url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/shonen-jump-1 |title=Shonen Jump, Volume 1 |first=John |last=Jakala |publisher=[[動畫新聞網|Anime News Network]] |date=2003-01-02 |accessdate=2008-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110211212951/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/shonen-jump-1 |archive-date=2011-02-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在之後的評論中，賈卡拉表示，《少年Jump》讓「美國漫畫相形失色」，將價錢相近的美國漫畫書拿來與雜誌一比，內容分量高下立分<ref name="Jakala2"/><ref name="Jakala3">{{cite web |url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/shonen-jump-3 |title=Shonen Jump, Volume 3 |first=John |last=Jakala |publisher=[[動畫新聞網|Anime News Network]] |date=2003-02-13 |accessdate=2008-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140712215852/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/shonen-jump-3 |archive-date=2014-07-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。不過他也指出，雜誌出到第3期時，一些連載漫畫的情節元素已經顯得沒有新意<ref name="Jakala3" />。網站Comic Book Bin的編者勒羅伊·朵瑞索（Leroy Douresseaux）稱讚雜誌的高CP值，並表示雜誌收錄的每篇漫畫都是「有頭有尾的完整故事，令人滿意」，而且都附有角色和劇情簡介，讀者就算錯過了某一期，依舊可以輕鬆跟上進度<ref name="Douresseaux">{{cite web |url=http://www.comicbookbin.com/shonenjumpvol01-08.html |title=SHONEN JUMP VOL. 1 #8 |first=Leroy |last=Douresseaux |publisher=Comic Book Bin |date=2003-10-12 |accessdate=2008-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081011105028/http://www.comicbookbin.com/shonenjumpvol01-08.html |archive-date=2008-10-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Douresseaux2">{{cite web |url=http://www.comicbookbin.com/shonenjump043.html |title=Shonen Jump: Vol. 4: Issue 7 |first=Leroy |last=Douresseaux |publisher=Comic Book Bin |date=2007-04-27 |accessdate=2008-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080804080935/http://www.comicbookbin.com/shonenjump043.html |archive-date=2008-08-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 爭議 ===

2004年4月，美國[[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]]的一位小學老師投訴，一名5年級學生在學校書展上買的《少年Jump》包含不當內容，引發爭議，有1萬8千份的雜誌遭到退回。碧日傳媒的發言人承認，雜誌內容明顯是針對年紀更大的讀者，確實不該出現在書展上，不過也反駁部分投訴內容是文化-{zh-hant:差異;zh-hans:差异}-或誤會。<ref>{{cite web|last=Reid|first=Calvin|url=https://www.publishersweekly.com/pw/print/20040405/28344-viz-manga-pulled-from-some-scholastic-fairs.html|title=Viz Manga Pulled from Some Scholastic Fairs|publisher=[[出版者周刊|Publishers Weekly]]|date=2004-04-02|accessdate=2020-07-28|archive-date=2020-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200829085245/https://www.publishersweekly.com/pw/print/20040405/28344-viz-manga-pulled-from-some-scholastic-fairs.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

